[Mirza2016ExpandingWP] proposes 30 manually-curated regular expression patterns for the hasChild predicate in Wikidata the extractions achieve more than 90% precision when compared with a small set of manually-labelled gold dataset and a larger KB available silver dataset. Cardinality assertions were extracted for 86.2k humans in Wikidata of which only 2.65% had complete hasChild statements.